name: Stickman Parachute: 3D Skydiving
description: Become a stickman skydiving champion!  As a stick skydiver, it will be your mission to avoid obstacles and.. not die : )  Fly through beautiful 3D levels and once you reach your target open your parachute! This stickman  parachuting game will test your reflexes and get you excited to try out skydiving,  and later parachute and BASE jumping for real, not just in the stick man world!
